Inside the DataTable component, after the existing summary rows (Total Income, Total Expenses, Yearly Net, Cumulative Net), add an "Investment Accounts" section. The exact implementation will depend on the existing row rendering pattern. The logic should:

1. Derive unique accounts from `accountBalances`: `const accounts = [...new Map(accountBalances.map(ab => [ab.modelId, ab.description])).entries()]`
